ISLAMABAD, June 21 (APP): President Dr. Arif Alvi on Monday expressed his grief over the sad demise of former Senator and leader of Pakhtoonkhwa Milli Awami Party (PkMAP) Usman Kakar.
The President in a message prayed for the departed soul and conveyed his condolences to the bereaved family.
